'''''Secrets of Naboo''''' is a paperback supplement to the [[Wizards of the Coast]] ''[[Star Wars Roleplaying Game]]''. It was written by [[Steve Miller]] and [[J.D. Wiker]] and published in [[February]] [[2001]]. Apart from information and game stats, the sourcebook also includes multiple short "story ideas" and the longer adventure "[[Peril on Naboo]]". The adventures "[[Operation: Clodhopper]]" and "[[Save the Mantaris!|Save the ''Mantaris!'']]", published at [[Wizards.com]], are also based on the book.

